lenders.occupational_info: In South Sardinia, you'll locate the lovely Chia Laguna Located on the isle of Sardinia, the Chia Laguna Resort offers luxurious accommodations that makes it a great vacation destination.  It offers grand sandy beaches as well as natural and lovely plant life and lagoons.   To offer you fitting accommodations, the resort has three independent hotels including the Hotel Laguna, the Hotel Chia Village, as well as the Hotel Oasi.  Each resort has a unique beach plus a variety of facilities and accommodations.     Each of the 34 hotel rooms in the Hotel Oasi come complete with views of the surrounding seascape.   You are able to select between the garden room variations or the different balcony suites on the top floors.    With terraces overlooking Chia bay, the Hotel Laguna boasts 82 spacious rooms.   The Hotel Chia Village plays host to clusters of private cottages which are still close enough to the resort facilities to help keep you amused.   The cottages are ideal for families which are searching for more space and also a bit of seclusion. During your stay, you will be able to take advantage of accommodations like satellite television, electronic secured safes, mini bars, and similar comforts.  When you're not in your room you'll be able to enjoy the number of restaurants, pools, sports facilities,health and beauty centers throughout the resort. Everything the resort offers is an effort to supply you with the best total experience from relaxation to gourmet dinners. You and your loved ones may also enjoy the guest-only reserved restaurant which offers a nightly cooking show alongside their delicious national dishes.There's also a restaurant dedicated to children and their tastes. The Sardinian resort has partnered with Design Holidays, making the affiliate a preferred travel business with the resort. This means that Design Holidays can give you discounts on holidays alongside their known affordable prices.  If you've decided to reserve a stay at the Chia Laguna Resort, you can get in contact with Design Holidays by calling 01444 87 2200 or by simply going to the resort's website.
